            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#606b76' fontname='Tableau Regular' fontsize='10'>A ratio above 1.0 means lifetime payouts exceed acquisition cost. Only LinkedIn outreach is profitable; paid search and social are deeply negative.</run>
